img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029fb29c6cbe9bf06a87e3c0e5993fa6645a448a","tid":1116036,"uid":124206,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T23:22:19.000Z","msg":"唔識廣東話扮識先最恐怖<br />\n題外話  早幾日去七仔贈值  攞張500蚊話增值100<br />\n收銀重複左幾次問係咪100 我豎埋手指先聽得明係100<br />\n之後收銀話驚自己聽錯  <br />\n應該係成日分唔清1同2"},{"pid":"642a6916e3bbd3d97a058506b7e8c7cc67448174","tid":1116036,"uid":96383,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T00:26:17.000Z","msg":"試過去診所睇醫生 <br />\n個醫生講啲廣東話唔正 又夾雜啲普通話<br />\n我話我頭痛 <br />\n講左幾次<br />\n佢都問左我啲問題，例如係咪成日痛個啲<br />\n又㩒下我肚，已經覺得唔對路<br />\n不過我以為可能關事<br />\n點知返到屋企啲藥全部係肚痛胃痛藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係香港發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間野係連鎖診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1836c7df319149d6f8051165b6c15ed5033545","tid":1116036,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T01:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc0d1441b4e30aea295da578b4ffc13594fa30a0","tid":1116036,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"上下不分<br />\n咩料"},{"pid":"31eb01827bf58487925494b20d20baeee804cbe7","tid":1116036,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"642a6916e3bbd3d97a058506b7e8c7cc67448174","tid":1116036,"uid":96383,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T00:26:17.000Z","msg":"試過去診所睇醫生 <br />\n個醫生講啲廣東話唔正 又夾雜啲普通話<br />\n我話我頭痛 <br />\n講左幾次<br />\n佢都問左我啲問題，例如係咪成日痛個啲<br />\n又㩒下我肚，已經覺得唔對路<br />\n不過我以為可能關事<br />\n點知返到屋企啲藥全部係肚痛胃痛藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係香港發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl